# Project Structure

Portal is a Next.js 15 application with a modern tech stack:

- **Frontend**: Next.js 15, React 19, TailwindCSS, shadcn/ui components
- **Backend**: Next.js API routes, tRPC, Next-Auth
- **Database**: PostgreSQL with Drizzle ORM
- **International**: next-intl for localization

## Key Directories

- `/app`: Next.js App Router structure
- `/components`: React components organized by section
- `/drizzle`: Database schema and migrations
- `/server`: tRPC routers and server-side logic
- `/lib`: Utility libraries and shared code
- `/public`: Static assets

## Main Entry Points

- [app/layout.tsx](mdc:app/layout.tsx): Root layout
- [app/[locale]/layout.tsx](mdc:app/[locale]/layout.tsx): Locale-specific layout
- [app/[locale]/(auth)/login/page.tsx](mdc:app/[locale]/(auth)/login/page.tsx): Login page
- [app/[locale]/dashboard/page.tsx](mdc:app/[locale]/dashboard/page.tsx): Dashboard home

## Authentication

- [auth.ts](mdc:auth.ts): Next-Auth configuration
- [app/api/auth/[...nextauth]/route.ts](mdc:app/api/auth/[...nextauth]/route.ts): Auth API routes

## Database

- [drizzle/schema.ts](mdc:drizzle/schema.ts): Database schema definitions
- [drizzle/relations.ts](mdc:drizzle/relations.ts): Table relationships
